sentence: Is EECS 281 an enforced prerequisite for anything ?
sentence-with-vars: Is department0 number0 an enforced prerequisite for anything ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias1.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias1.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE AS COURSEalias1 , COURSE_PREREQUISITE AS COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.PRE_COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 281 AND COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.COURSE_ID ;
